# FiberSync - Testing Plan

This document outlines the current and planned unit tests across our backend and frontend.
Note: Tests currently marked as skipped or commented out are retained in the codebase for future repair and to be reintegrated. 
Once other features have been implemented we'll begin working to resolve database state issues that interfere with consistent test behavior.


